OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of rain will spread
OL,6,Fsoutheastwards, bringing some heavy
OL,7,Fbursts from late morning with a risk
OL,8,Fof thunder. Sunny spells then develop
OL,9,Fduring the afternoon, but also
OL,10,Fscattered, possibly heavy showers.
OL,11,FWind easing. Cool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy showers clearing
OL,14,Feastern parts, then sunny spells for
OL,15,Fmany this evening. A dry night follows
OL,16,Fwith clear spells, but showers into
OL,17,Fwestern parts by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
