OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA mixture of sunny spells and
OL,6,Fblustery showers on Tuesday, with a
OL,7,Frisk of hail and thunder. Feeling cool
OL,8,Ffor the time of year.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,11,FSunshine and showers Wednesday with a
OL,12,Frisk of thunder. Rain arriving during
OL,13,FThursday. Friday, sunny spells perhaps
OL,14,Fwith rain or showers. Breezy at times.
OL,15,FRather cool, trending nearer normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
